>> time required: 1 hours
>> course: main

Add drained @ricotta{500%g}; either
Drain over night OR
Spread over a few layers of paper towels and sandwich between a several more paper towel and press firmly
Put cheese in a bowl and add @egg{1} and mix well
Slowly add @flour tipo 00{300%g} to the mixture also
Add @pecorino{4%tbsp} to the mixture
Once it comes together knead it until softens and not sticky
Create a ball and let rest ~{10%minutes}
Make gnocchi
